title: Looking for silver players keen to climb dynamic queue
body:
Looking to find a couple of players who are looking to get out of silver using dynamic queue with myself and a friend. Confident solid top laners, supports or junglers ideal. 
Skype or team speak would also make the dynamic q a lot more effective.
Reply here if interested cheers lads
or Add me in game: Aus Dave

replies.body:
I'm interested
I'm a 15 yr old Mid and top main, but can play jg and sup
I can also skype
I am interested, currently a Silver 5 support main look forward to hearing from you.
YES im keen Silver 5 JG Main
Hello, I can go everywhere, I am best at all roles except support, I pref like to have 4 supps on my team at all times.
I'll add you in game, or you can add me to show your committed!
